I think he captured with the knight so he could get rid of the knight I am about to put on the d5 outpost.  However, in doing so I am able to capture his knight with my e pawn.   That pawn will be almost impossible to remove.  Once he pushes his b and f pawns I'll have an outpost on c6 and more importantly on e6.  It takes me a while to plop a piece on e6 but I do.
